action.action-desc: Mr. Amodei introduced the following bill; which was referred to the Committee on Natural Resources

form.official-title: To nullify Public Land Order No. 7921, withdrawing certain land in the Railroad Valley of Nye County, Nevada, from mineral entry.

section.text: Public Land Order No. 7921 (88 Fed. Reg. 25682, relating to the withdrawal of public land for satellite calibration in Railroad Valley; Nye County, Nevada) shall have no force or effect.
